## Example 2 — Simplify Expressions with the Quotient Property

### a. `cuberoot((24a^6)/125)`

`= cuberoot(24a^6) / cuberoot(125)`

`= cuberoot(2^3 * 3 * (a^2)^3) / cuberoot(5^3)`

`= 2a^2 cuberoot(3) / 5`

### b. `fourthroot((80y^14)/(256z^4))`

`= fourthroot(80y^14) / fourthroot(256z^4)`

Factor into fourth powers and simplify:

`= |y^3| fourthroot(5y^2) / (2z)`

